# iSida Discord Bot

**iSida** is a professional moderation Discord bot built with `discord.py` and MongoDB. It provides slash commands for server moderation, anti-spam/anti-link/anti-mass-mention protection, and full logging capabilities.

> **Web Dashboard**: [https://isida-dashboard.onrender.com](https://isida-dashboard.onrender.com)  
> Use the dashboard to view warnings, moderation logs, and manage your servers from your browser.

---

## ✨ Features

- **Slash Commands Only** – All commands are registered as application commands (no prefix mess).
- **Moderation Commands**: `/kick`, `/ban`, `/unban`, `/warn`, `/removewarn`, `/warnings`, `/clear`, `/slowmode`, `/lockdown`, `/unlock`
- **Auto‑Moderation**: Anti‑spam (5 messages / 5 seconds), anti‑Discord invite links, anti‑mass‑mention (max 5 mentions).
- **Mod Logging**: Every moderation action is logged to a dedicated channel with rich embeds.
- **MongoDB Storage**: Warnings, infractions, and guild configurations are persisted.
- **User‑Friendly Embeds**: All responses use clean, colored embeds with consistent styling.
- **Interactive Help**: `/help` dynamically lists all available commands grouped by category.
- **Easy Deployment**: Ready for Railway or any Python host with `requirements.txt` and `Procfile`.

---

## 🛠️ Commands Overview

| Command         | Description                                                                   | Required Permission     |
|----------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------|
| `/kick`        | Kick a member from the server.                                                | Kick Members            |
| `/ban`         | Ban a user (by ID or mention).                                                | Ban Members             |
| `/unban`       | Unban a user by their ID.                                                     | Ban Members             |
| `/warn`        | Issue a warning to a member.                                                  | Moderate Members        |
| `/removewarn`  | Remove a warning using its MongoDB ObjectId.                                  | Moderate Members        |
| `/warnings`    | List all warnings for a specific member.                                      | Moderate Members        |
| `/clear`       | Delete up to 100 messages (optionally filter by member).                      | Manage Messages         |
| `/slowmode`    | Set slowmode delay (0–21600 seconds) for the channel.                         | Manage Channels         |
| `/lockdown`    | Lock the current channel (prevent @everyone from sending).                    | Manage Channels         |
| `/unlock`      | Unlock the current channel.                                                   | Manage Channels         |
| `/setmodlog`   | Set a channel where all moderation logs will be sent.                         | Administrator           |
| `/help`        | Show all available slash commands in a categorized embed.                     | None (everyone)         |

